rating_comment: Booking this place is a decision you won't regret. The property boasts a tasteful decor that instantly makes you feel at home. Allan, the host, is exceptionally responsive, ensuring a seamless experience. The attention to detail in the decor and amenities adds an extra layer of comfort. The location is convenient, and the overall ambiance makes it a standout choice. Treat it as more than just an airbnb; make it your home away from home, where every detail is designed for your utmost satisfaction.
well maintained property, and very cooperative staff
